---
title: Bacon, Sweetcorn & Carrot Noodle Soup with Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: Whether it be in warm weather or cold weather, soup always sits well at dinner time. The big benefit of a soup is you
can taste everything in one slurp, like the veggies, ginger and mushroom seasoning with pops of bacon all pulled in
together by the carrot noodles. See for yourself and get slurping!

